---
title: Beef & Bacon Cornish-Style Pasties with Apple Salad & Tomato Relish
description: This pastry delight brings all the warmth and comfort of a pie into a fun handheld meal! Packed with succulent beef, golden
nuggets of bacon, and a hearty mix of veggies, this flaky masterpiece is a winner in our eyes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66889faddea0224ab0733546-c34b69db.jpeg
